# ProxyFAQs Cloudflare Pages Redirects

# Force HTTPS
http://proxyfaqs.com/* https://proxyfaqs.com/:splat
http://www.proxyfaqs.com/* https://proxyfaqs.com/:splat
https://www.proxyfaqs.com/* https://proxyfaqs.com/:splat

# API health check
/health /api/health 200

# Preserve method/body for API callers that omit the trailing slash
/api/view /api/view/ 307
